attributes.description: Overview dashboard for AWS Lambda showcasing execution and billed duration, memory usage, and detailed function logs per invocation.

params.markdown:
### AWS Lambda logs

This dashboard highlights key AWS Lambda metrics and logs such as:

- Execution duration and billed duration

- Memory allocation and usage

- Function logs for each invocation

embeddableConfig.description: The time taken to initialize the Lambda execution environment during a cold start.
The time the lambda function handler method spent processing the event.
The total time billed for the invocation
The amount of memory allocated to your Lambda function during its configuration.
The peak amount of memory utilised by the AWS Lambda function during a specific invocation.
The amount of memory allocated to your Lambda function during its configuration.
